sec.p:
The Inhibitory Effect Sigmoid Emax Model in the WinNonlin software (version 5.2.1, Pharsight, St. Louis, MO, USA) was used to simulate the relationship between indexes AUC/MIC, Cmax/MIC of ENR, and in vivo effectiveness.
